Name:           priv_wrapper
Version:        1.0.1
Release:        5%{?dist}

Summary:        A library to disable resource limits and other privilege dropping
License:        GPLv3+
Url:            http://cwrap.org/

Source0:        https://ftp.samba.org/pub/cwrap/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
Source1:        https://ftp.samba.org/pub/cwrap/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz.asc
